<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau thieng, ka paucham ngai tha'n,
 Ka lung u-ah chengin;
 Na hehpihna tawh hungkum in,
 Aw Thagau Thieng, hungin!

[V2]
 2. Vak bangin ka kawmah hungin,
 Ka taksap ei hilh in;
 Hinna lampi-ah ei puiin,
 Mi dik cheng chiehna ah.

[V3]
 3. Mei bangin hung kilak inla,
 Kithawih na mei bangin;
 Ka hinnau kithawih na hi hen,
 Ka Hukdampau min in.

[V4]
 4. Daitui bang hungkie'n vang ei pie'n,
 Zie kipiekna hun hin;
 Gam gawmun haw chuh chap chekin,
 Nang bangin kipak hen.

[V5]
 5. Vakhu bang tha zakin hungin,
 Hehpih muonna tha chuh;
 Leia Na Sapchuomte vangpie'n,
 Chunga Sapchuom bangin.

[V6]
 6. Huih bangin hungin, thawmgi tawh,
 Penticost hehpihna;
 Mihiem chengin a muhna di'n,
 Na mel lopi zie chuh.</lyrics>
<title>SPIRIT DIVINE ATTEND OUR PRAYERS</title>
</song>